# Global Superstore – Data Cleaning & Formatting (Excel)

## Project Overview
This project focuses on cleaning and formatting the Global Superstore dataset using Microsoft Excel.
The objective is to transform raw, messy data into a clean and analysis-ready dataset.

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Power Query
- Excel built-in functions

## Dataset
- Global Superstore dataset
- Contains sales, customer, product, and regional data

## Data Cleaning Steps Performed
- Removed duplicate records
- Handled missing and blank values
- Standardized text fields (TRIM, PROPER)
- Corrected date and numeric formats
- Renamed columns for clarity
- Maintained raw and cleaned data separately

## Files in Repository
- Raw_Data.xlsx – Original dataset
- Cleaned_Data.xlsx – Cleaned and formatted dataset
- cleaned_dataset.csv – Final cleaned data in CSV format

## Outcome
The cleaned dataset is ready for further analysis and visualization.
